game

Class Game

  • Object
    • Check
      • Game
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MasterMind, MoreLess

    public abstract class Game
extends Check
    This is the Model Application. it requires 2 players and the methods return a status that can be used in the controller for switching It's a child of the Check class what allows to check the user's inputs.
    Author:
    Xavier.Lamourec
